      "id": "shipment_evidence_text",
      "x": 1542.445113453574,
      "y": 748.1839599203121,
      "width": 562.5,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Shipment lifecycle evidence\nShipmentLifecycleService.TryCreateForOrderAsync\nSkip if not GHN delivery\nReuse existing shipment unless status is FailedToCreate\nCreatePending -> call GHN -> MarkCreated or MarkCreateFailed\nAdmin controls: create, requote, sync, cancel, update note",
      "originalText": "Shipment lifecycle evidence\nShipmentLifecycleService.TryCreateForOrderAsync\nSkip if not GHN delivery\nReuse existing shipment unless status is FailedToCreate\nCreatePending -> call GHN -> MarkCreated or MarkCreateFailed\nAdmin controls: create, requote, sync, cancel, update note",
