    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "race_evidence_text",
      "x": 145,
      "y": 1305,
      "width": 839.1959957433452,
      "height": 164.8946517951836,
      "text": "Race-safety evidence\nPOST /api/v1/payments/stripe/reconcile requires SessionId or CheckoutDraftId\nIf payment already exists locally, return committed result\nIf provider says paid, finalize using paymentIntentId and chargeId\nWebhook handling is idempotent and audits every attempt\nDuplicate success first checks payment by Stripe session id\nDbUpdateException fallback reloads committed payment after a race",
      "originalText": "Race-safety evidence\nPOST /api/v1/payments/stripe/reconcile requires SessionId or CheckoutDraftId\nIf payment already exists locally, return committed result\nIf provider says paid, finalize using paymentIntentId and chargeId\nWebhook handling is idempotent and audits every attempt\nDuplicate success first checks payment by Stripe session id\nDbUpdateException fallback reloads committed payment after a race",
      "fontSize": 18.845103062306688,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
