      "height": 227.33864729105773,
      "text": "GHN evidence\nPOST /api/v1/shipping/ghn/webhook\nSynthetic id uses event type, status, time, provider code, and\nclient order code\nIf shipment is missing, audit row becomes shipment_not_found\nCurrent note: signature verification is not implemented here\nCustomer and admin read model: GET /api/v1/shipping/orders/\n{orderId}\nBackground side flow: OrderAutoCompleteJob advances stale\nInDelivery orders to Delivered",
      "originalText": "GHN evidence\nPOST /api/v1/shipping/ghn/webhook\nSynthetic id uses event type, status, time, provider code, and client order code\nIf shipment is missing, audit row becomes shipment_not_found\nCurrent note: signature verification is not implemented here\nCustomer and admin read model: GET /api/v1/shipping/orders/{orderId}\nBackground side flow: OrderAutoCompleteJob advances stale InDelivery orders to Delivered",
